        "data": "<h2 id=\"h_01J01893X1MQ4BWP2ARVWST629\">Liferay SaaS Security Alert: March 2020</h2>\n\n<p><span>The following issue may compromise the security of your Liferay SaaS environment.</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"h_01J01893X184ZQH073G5S761VF\">Vulnerability Information</h2>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/articles/360041305692\" target=\"_self\">29-VULN (LSV-545)</a>: Unauthenticated Remote code execution via JSONWS</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Please see the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https://help.liferay.com/hc/en-us/articles/360018875952#DXP-cloud\">Liferay SaaS Security Advisories</a></span> section for more information on the vulnerability.</p>"
      },
